OL,3,CFlu warnings from NHS chiefs in
OL,4,CCumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FNHS chiefs are warning people about
OL,7,Fthe risk of flu following a spike in
OL,8,Fhospital admissions.
OL,10,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway says it's
OL,11,Fdealing with higher numbers of flu-
OL,12,Frelated hospital admissions than
OL,13,Fexpected for this time of year and has
OL,14,Fplaced restrictions on visitor numbers.
