OL,3,CFlu warnings from NHS chiefs in
OL,4,CCumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FKenneth Donaldson, Director of
OL,7,FMedical, NHS Dumfries and Galloway:
OL,8,F"Most years we will see a bit of a
OL,9,Fspike in flu this year has been a
OL,10,Flittle unusual as flu as come a little
OL,11,Fearlier and coincided with Christmas
OL,12,Fand people getting together.
OL,14,F"What we are advising people is that
OL,15,Fat the moment we have restricted
OL,16,Fvisiting in certain areas to essential
OL,17,Fvisiting only. We are trying to
OL,18,Fencourage people, particularly if you
OL,19,Fare not feeling well to not come into
OL,20,Fhospital to visit loved ones.
