OL,3,CFlu warnings from NHS chiefs in
OL,4,CCumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,F"Normally visiting would be two people
OL,7,Fper person but we are saying contact
OL,8,Fthe ward before you come and if it is
OL,9,Fnot viewed to be essential then we
OL,10,Fwould ask not to come at this moment.
OL,12,F"Over the last weekend A&E and our
OL,13,Fmedical admissions were busy and we
OL,14,Fdid see an increase in flu admissions,
OL,15,Fparticularly amongst the elderly.
OL,16,FThankfully that has settled down but
OL,17,Fwe are going back into a public
OL,18,Fholiday and a long weekend to come."
