OL,3,CFlu warnings from NHS chiefs in
OL,4,CCumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FNorth Cumbria Integrated Care Trust
OL,7,Fsay there are currently almost 100
OL,8,Fpeople in its hospitals with flu.
OL,10,FClive Graham, Director of Infection,
OL,11,FPrevention & Control, North Cumbria
OL,12,FIntegrated Care, said: "We are seeing
OL,13,Fa lot of flu cases at the moment. Most
OL,14,Fof them are coming in from the
OL,15,Fcommunity so it really is a busy time
OL,16,Fof year.
