OL,3,CFlu warnings from NHS chiefs in
OL,4,CCumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,F"We have decided as a precautionary
OL,7,Fmeasure to put some visitor
OL,8,Frestrictions in place. This is to
OL,9,Fminimise the risk of spreading the flu
OL,10,Fthroughout the hospital and to protect
OL,11,Fvisitors who could potentially pick up
OL,12,Fthe flu when visiting their loved
OL,13,Fones."
